features: Desk with Hutch & Monitor Riser - 2 top hutch reduce tabletop clutter, an ideal place to set up small printers, files, and plants. The monitor riser can hold 3-4 monitors and keep you at eye level for comfortable viewing while increasing more space for other office supplies

Computer Desk with Charging Port - Our charging station includes 4-Outlets, 2 USB Ports and 1 Type-C Ports to provide power for up to 7 devices simultaneously. Power outlet allows you to charge cell phones, tablets, notebook, which provides a great convenience to your life when you are working or playing games

Smart and Surrounded LED Strips - This home office desk boasts built-in LED lighting with 7 main colors, 12 scene modes, 3 speed levels adjustment, and 3 brightness modes to create a stunning ambiance. The controller is installed on the monitor stand, convenient to change the light when you are working

2-In-1 L Shaped Design - Become a 58.3” L-shaped corner desk with storage shelves that fits perfectly in small spaces while providing maximum space. Or you can change to a 82.7" extra long desk with a storage stand that fits in large space while providing a 2-person seat and no interference

Super Sturdy & Stable Construction - The 2 spacious desktops are supported by a strong stainless steel frame not only looks great, but also features superior durability and stability. Adjustable leg pads can keep the desk stable on uneven floor, protect the floor from scratches and prolong the use time

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I am so in love and beyond happy with my purchase!
reviews.reviewText: I really wanted to wait until I had the time to make a video of the whole desk put together, and show everyone interested in this desk, just how beautiful it is but I will just come back and update my review with a video soon.My order came on time and my desk was packaged with care and easy to take out the box. Everything as described, came inside the box and the directions were clear and easy for me to go over and to read.Side note:I had to really take my time with putting everything together because at first, it looked like there were holes missing but it was just my perception. ALL HOLES ARE ACTUALLY THERE!! JUST TAKE YOUR TIME AND PAY ATTENTION!!.When I finally put the desk together, I was just incomplete awe at how beautiful it looked and for the low great price it was, I just felt lucky.It is sturdy and definitely holds it's weight. It is the right size for me in all aspects, leg room long and tall, just perfect. I chose the color white and it goes great with my white gaming chair.The control system for the lights is easy to learn/use and the lights with many different modes are bright and vibrant.The middle and top shelves are such a great add on, so that is a major plus for me. However, I do wish that the desk "without the monitor shelve" had two shelves so that I could put my other gaming systems on but other then that, I am truly happy with my purchase!!.I recommend thus desk to whoever wants to buy an amazing desk for a price.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Work Desk and Space Saver
reviews.reviewText: This is a great table for anyone needing space but also configurability. The hutch provides ample extra space to store various items such as figures, HDDs, Docks, and the hutch is also great for monitors as I use mine for it. Honestly, this table was a pain to assemble at time but a great table that's pretty sturdy, quite stylish in a minimalistic way and has tons of display / storage space. I love that this table can be configured into either an L shape or something longer if you want / need it. If you're looking for a table with plenty of working space and then some, honestly, pull the trigger, especially at the price. The included LED lights are also quite bright and really cool functionality even if they are "manual" (The control for the lights are built into the table).

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: My 13 year old loves the desk. The leds are bright and look really neat. The wood looks good and not cheap.overall feels sturdy and was not awful to put together. He is into making his own fishing baits and the leds make it look cool

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 14, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Really awesome desk
reviews.reviewText: After looking at probably 200+ desks for probably 4 hours over 2 days I found this one. I was looking for something really specific and this fit the bill. I was REALLY worried it was gonna turn out to be crap though because it only had a few reviews.This desk is great, especially since you can assemble it a few different ways. I thought the instructions were great, and it took me around 50 minutes to put it together & I'm extremely mechanically inclined. That being said, if your good with your hands maybe have someone help you. I also used an impact and allen socket instead of the crap allen keys that always come with furniture.The only thing that kinda sucks is the wood is all compressed wood, but all the furniture these days is, and this is actually still very sturdy.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Amazing for the price!
reviews.reviewText: I've been building cheap target and wal mart furniture for years and this is the first "cheap" type thing I've ever purchased that is sturdy and I feel like will last a long time. Definitely not something I'd un-build to move for any reason, but for $100 its absolutely perfect for my daughter and she loves that the lights change to lots of colors. It's a hit with both of us. Pro tip the box is heavy so make sure you have someone to help you when it gets delivered.
